body: Hi, I just started learning ladybug. Recently, I tried to make a grid-based analysis with manually assigned windows. However, after I finished battery map based on tutorial file 006_Parametric_GridBasedAnalysis, the simulation did not run. Could you please help me take a look what may be wrong? Honey bee did not response after I switch the boolean toggles.
